/// Description: Searches for product mentions across various platforms.

When @trigger search_mentions arrives:
  • Use the @tool web_search to find mentions of "OurProduct"
  • Use the @tool social_media_search to find social media mentions
  • Use the @tool news_search to find news articles mentioning the product
  • Return all findings as structured data
  • If more than 10 mentions found, hand over to flows #high_volume_alert